{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1b6d4fcc8b","title":"对一篇评中苏分岐的文章的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4f7db7a5ea","index":0,"year":1963,"month":7,"day":31,"articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"7626190ffb","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指新华社1963年7月31日《参考资料》上刊载的《束埔寨电讯报》发表的《赫鲁晓夫是否改变态度了？》一文。文章指出，在中苏分岐中，苏联歪曲了中国关于核战争问题的观点，在和平共处问题上对中国的指责怡恰和西方国家不谋而合。人们本来希望中苏之间取得妥协，但赫鲁晓夫同西方接近的既成事实，使这种希望完全化为乌有。这篇文章在1963年8月1日《人民日报》上发表。"},{"id":"49abd07a10","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"吴冷西，当时任新华通讯社社长、《人民日报》总编辑。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f0bccef8d7","type":"title","text":"对一篇评中苏分岐的文章\"的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b"},{"id":"7626190ffb","type":"paragraph","text":"吴冷西响志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b"},{"id":"49abd07a10","type":"paragraph","text":"这篇文章，似可发表。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b"},{"id":"6de400a8f5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b"},{"id":"0a65e06ded","type":"paragraph","text":"七月册一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b"},{"id":"2515668569","type":"paragraph","text":"全文都好。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b"}],"page":{"id":"f09827a873","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"1b6d4fcc8b","start":489,"end":489}}}},"__N_SSG":true}